article.description: Monica Wright scored 22 points and Lyndra Littles added a season-high 21 to lead Virginia (No. 15 ESPN/USA Today, No. 16 AP) to an 83-38 victory over Rider in the Cavalier Classic.
article.headline: Virginia advances to championship game of Cavalier Classic
article.linkText: Virginia cruises past Rider in Cavalier Classic
article.story:
CHARLOTTESVILLE, Va. -- Monica Wright scored 22 points and Lyndra Littles added a season-high 21 to lead Virginia (No. 15 ESPN/USA Today, No. 16 AP) to an 83-38 victory over Rider on Sunday in the Cavalier Classic.

It was the seventh straight game Wright has topped 20 points. She also had six steals.

The Cavaliers (10-2) never trailed, building a 48-19 halftime lead behind 16 first-half points from Littles and 12 from Wright.

Virginia will face Louisiana Tech in the championship game on Monday.

Amanda Sepulveda scored 14 to lead Rider (2-8).
